This small beach town is a popular destination for Santiaguinos and Argentines from Mendoza in the summer months of Jaunary and February. The most "popular" section of the beach is the Quinta Sector to the north where most of the young, fashionable people can be found.
By car or take a bus from the Plaza de Armas in Viña del Mar to Reñaca. It is located about 15 minutes up the coast from the center of Viña on the way to Con Con.
